l world, our results also show that it is possible to\nimplement secret sharing over small fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2020 06:21:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 12:59:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-31"}
