 is watching. But if we focus on the effect of recent legislative\nchanges in the area of electronic surveillance we can clearly see that the\nOrwellian dystopia is already here, and we are living it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2020 08:33:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-27"}
