 is modestly increased from 5.1 % to 5.4 %. We relate these\nimprovements to the increased conductivity of the emissive layer, and to the\nbetter charge balance of the electrically injected carriers. In this respect,\nwe performed ultraviolet photoelectron spectroscopy (UPS) to obtain deeper\ninsight in the band alignment of the LED structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2020 10:16:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-27"}
