ograming language. Our results confirm that deep representation of\nsource code and the active feedback loop is an assuring approach for predicting\nsecurity and other vulnerabilities present in the code.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2020 13:18:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-28"}
